message.body: Thinking about you and little Luci! I can't wait for you to go to Laura's next week! And me too on Sunday!!! What happened to May?! :)
Tell me abt it! Cant believe paz is already halfway thru 1st yr. Lookin 4ward 2 ny too! U goin up sun morn?
Can I come over sometime and hold Paz before she's too heavy? :) I am around Mondays after work and Saturday and Sunday afternoons. Let me know if you're free!
